/** \page Blinking Blinking
 *
 * The Blinking example shows how to use OpenSEK and OpenDRV (Dio) to read the
 * state of two buttons and to blink 2 leds. The example can work in any boards
 * with at least 2 buttons and 2 leds. At the moment this example runs in the
 * following boards:
 *		- Olimex lpc-e2468
 *
 * 1.- How to configure my Makefile for this example
 *
 * Edit the root Makefile and set the following variables to the indicated values:
 *
 * BOARD = lpc-e2468
 *
 * MODS +=	examples/Blinking			\
 *				OpenGEN						\
 *				OpenDRV						\
 *				OpenSEK
 *
 */

